Package: SimpLin
Type: Package
Title: Simple Linear Regression via RcppArmadillo
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Mayson", family = "Zhang", email = "mayson.zhang18@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Maintainer: Mayson Zhang <mayson.zhang18@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a fast simple linear regression (y ~ x) with estimates, standard errors,
    95% confidence intervals, residuals, and fitted values, implemented in C++ via Rcpp
    and RcppArmadillo. Includes an R wrapper with validation and a vignette.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports: Rcpp
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, ggplot2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
